# MMS Migration Status

Rules describe **target architecture**. Open gaps below — fix when the task covers them.

| Area | Current state | Target (rules) |
|------|---------------|----------------|
| Hardcoded labels/colours | Widespread in modules | Config/registry + `t()` — `mms-i18n.mdc` |
| Contact `uiStrings` map | Contacts module toasts/labels | New copy → `appTranslations` + `t()`; no new `uiStrings` keys |
| TanStack Query | Students + contacts + workspace registry + auth; most modules still localStorage | New REST resources Query-first — `mms-query.mdc` |
| `can()` permissions hook | Shipped; Enrollments + Attendance wired; registry partial | Full registry-driven matrix — `mms-rbac.mdc` |
| Inline `role ===` checks | Dashboard widget filtering uses `resolveDashboardPersona(can)`; `useViewerRole` derives from `can()` | Full registry-driven matrix — `mms-rbac.mdc` |
| Custom tab provisioning | JSON document store only | Table + migration + CRUD per custom tab — `mms-fields.mdc` |
| WebSockets | Not implemented | Replace polling for server push — `mms-core.mdc` |
| Work/Reports sub-tabs | Residual inline bars in deep components | `SubTabBar` per `mms-ui-tabs.mdc` |
| `category="academic"` in reports/KPI | Removed from module pages | Module-specific categories only (`mms-module-isolation.mdc`) |
| Legacy entity forms | ObligationModal, some detail drawers | `FormModal` — `mms-ui-forms.mdc` |
| Status colours inline | Residual in chart color maps | `StatusBadge` + semantic tokens — `mms-ui-visual.mdc` |
| Automated tests | Shared + backend (auth, rbac, health, security); frontend apiClient + hooks; Playwright smoke in CI `e2e/` | Expand Playwright for login/onboard — `mms-testing.mdc` |
| Server-first data | Students + contacts Query-first; most modules localStorage primary | Query + API authoritative for new modules — `mms-data-layer.mdc` |
| Per-entity REST API | `/api/students` + `/api/contacts` CRUD; generic `/api/db` for rest | Resource routes + validation per domain — `mms-backend.mdc` |
| Internal `fetch('/api/...')` | External OAuth only | All MMS API via `apiClient` — `mms-frontend.mdc` |
| JWT in localStorage | Removed — httpOnly cookies only; `apiClient` has no token reads | — resolved |
| Client error reporting | Console/toasts only | Sentry or equivalent — `mms-observability.mdc` |
| Global a11y pass | Partial (dropdowns only) | WCAG baseline on new UI — `mms-a11y.mdc` |

